All Classes

  • Class Description
    CompressFactory
    This class CompressFactory makes use of Factory design pattern Creates object at runtime Creates object for TextCompressionStrategy if string is Text Creates object for ImageCompressionStrategy if string is image
    CompressionApplicationMain
    This is the main compression application which perform compression for a text or image file.
    CompressionStrategy
    This interface CompressionStrategy has compress method declaration for any algorithm to be inherited and reuse it later.
    ImageCompressionStrategy
    This class TextCompressionStrategy makes use of Strategy pattern by inheriting the interface CompressionStrategy
    TextCompressionStrategy
    This class TextCompressionStrategy makes use of Strategy pattern by inheriting the interface CompressionStrategy This class object will be called if input file is Text file
    Utils
    This class Utils has methods to provide the extension of the input file and provide output file with modified input file name and output path same as same file path.
